## Context

RDJ-26561 R&R (tracker 0274), remarks R1-16a, R1-16c. Two localized wording
fixes:

1. (R1-16a) The paper says OpenAlex indexes RePEc; it also indexes other
   economics working-paper series (NBER, MPRA, …) — say so up front for the
   uninformed reader.
2. (R1-16c) "the five smaller sources add non-English, institutional, and
   pedagogical coverage that OpenAlex alone does not provide" misleads:
   OpenAlex does include non-English sources. Reword to claim only the
   *incremental* coverage the smaller sources add.

